QuestData.Title: THAELIN!
QuestData.Description: That little...!$B$B<Yrel tries to maintain her composure.>$B$BThaelin Darkanvil sent us a shipment. It was supposed to be engineering parts.$B$BInstead, when we just opened one of the crates, out popped a baby goren. Do you know how destructive those things are?$B$BAnd, of course, the one baby immediately set about letting all the other ones loose.$B$BWant to help me get some revenge?
QuestData.CompletionText: Did you round them all up?
QuestData.RewardText: Outstanding.$B$B<Vindicator Yrel beckons you closer so that the two of you can conspire.>
